 "https://twitter.com/emtiadefteri", "id": "1112665770301878272", "name": "EmtiaDefteri", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2024897154503069696/JAdWz5zV_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1112665770301878272/1773852162", "description": "", "location": "", "followers": 54735, "following": 379, "status": "", "canDm": true, "canMediaTag": false, "createdAt": "Mon Apr 01 10:39:26 +0000 2019", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 1056, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 1168, "statusesCount": 7955, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": [], "profile_bio": {"description": "Metal, Tar\u0131m, Enerji Notlar\u0131 - Detaylar, veriler, de\u011ferlendirmeler i\u00e7in l\u00fctfen abone olun.", "entities": {"description": {}, "url": {"urls": [{"display_url": "emtiadefteri.com", "expanded_url": "http://emtiadefteri.com", "indices": [0, 23], "url": "https://t.co/YNvZQcDylG"}]}}}, "isAutomated": false, "automatedBy": null}, "extendedEntities": {}, "card": null, "place": {}, "entities": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [], "timestamps": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": []}, "quoted_tweet": null, "retweeted_tweet": null, "isLimitedReply": false, "communityInfo": null, "article": null}, {"type": "tweet", "id": "2050893444847919365", "url": "https://x.com/0xKasper_/status/2050893444847919365", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/0xKasper_/status/2050893444847919365", "text": "Et si ce m\u00e9tal nous sauvait d\u2019une crise \u00e9conomique ?\n\nOn parle d\u2019un m\u00e9tal longtemps ignor\u00e9, qui pourrait devenir cl\u00e9 dans la prochaine phase de croissance technologique.\n\nAujourd\u2019hui, l\u2019IA fait exploser la demande en \u00e9nergie. L\u2019entra\u00eenement des mod\u00e8les et les data centers tournent en continu ce qui cr\u00e9e une pression \u00e9norme sur les infrastructures \u00e9lectriques ( j\u2019avais fait un article dessus avec de super r\u00e9sultats )\n\nCe m\u00e9tal est une alternative cr\u00e9dible face \u00e0 l\u2019uranium. Il est environ 3 \u00e0 4 fois plus abondant et pr\u00e9sente des propri\u00e9t\u00e9s int\u00e9ressantes de stabilit\u00e9 et de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 en r\u00e9acteur. L\u00e0 o\u00f9 l\u2019uranium est aujourd\u2019hui la norme, il pourrait offrir une production d\u2019\u00e9nergie plus durable et mieux adapt\u00e9e aux besoins continus de l\u2019IA qui est une narrative devenu trop importante dans l\u2019\u00e9conomie pour \u00e9chouer d\u2019o\u00f9 le titre. \n\nCertains commencent d\u00e9j\u00e0 \u00e0 se positionner sur cette narrative via NuScale Power $SMR ou Cameco $CCJ.\n\nEn parall\u00e8le, TerraPower soutenue par Bill Gates anticipe aussi ce virage.\n\nLa Chine investit d\u00e9j\u00e0 \u00e0 long terme sur cette ressource avec une logique de domination \u00e9nerg\u00e9tique consciente que l\u2019\u00e9nergie sera le nerf de cette guerre.\n\nCe m\u00e9tal, c\u2019est le Thorium.\n\nAujourd\u2019hui, la narrative n\u2019est pas encore mature, cherche les gagnants de demain et les financements ne sont pas encore au rendez-vous mais s\u2019y int\u00e9resser d\u00e8s maintenant, c\u2019est commencer \u00e0 construire une vrai th\u00e8se sur un march\u00e9 qui sera massif \u00e0 terme.", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 1, "replyCount": 3, "likeCount": 18, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 1432, "createdAt": "Sun May 03 11:01:15 +0000 2026", "lang": "fr", "bookmarkCount": 26, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2050893444847919365", "displayTextRange": [0, 272], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "0xKasper_", "url": "https://x.com/0xKasper_", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/0xKasper_", "id": "1742126777907007488", "name": "Kasper", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2050318911371919360/EDIaylkW_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1742126777907007488/1777669097", "description": "", "location": "", "followers": 6290, "following": 81, "status": "", "canDm": true, "canMediaTag": false, "createdAt": "Tue Jan 02 10:12:51 +0000 2024", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 11359, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 1474, "statusesCount": 6947, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": ["2034207290484564357"], "profile_bio": {"description": "I don\u2019t lose money, I just provide liquidity when needed.\nCrypto | Bourse | IA enjoyerrrr", "entities": {"description": {}}}, "isAutomated": false, "automatedBy": null}, "extendedEntities": {"media": [{"display_url": "pic.twitter.com/kwWwPLGrXH", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/0xKasper_/status/2050893444847919365/photo/1", "ext_media_availability": {"status": "Available"}, "features": {"large": {"faces": []}, "orig": {"faces": []}}, "id_str": "2050893439449927680", "indices": [273, 296], "media_key": "3_2050893439449927680", "media_results": {"id": "QXBpTWVkaWFSZXN1bHRzOgwAAQoAARx2PLeSl5AACgACHHY8uNRWYQUAAA==", "result": {"__typename": "ApiMedia", "id": "QXBpTWVkaWE6DAABCgABHHY8t5KXkAAKAAIcdjy41FZhBQAA", "media_key": "3_2050893439449927680"}}, "media_url_https": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HHY8t5KXkAAXyHx.jpg", "original_info": {"focus_rects": [{"h": 672, "w": 1200, "x": 0, "y": 128}, {"h": 800, "w": 800, "x": 0, "y": 0}, {"h": 800, "w": 702, "x": 0, "y": 0}, {"h": 800, "w": 400, "x": 0, "y": 0}, {"h": 800, "w": 1200, "x": 0, "y": 0}], "height": 800, "width": 1200}, "sizes": {"large": {"h": 800, "w": 1200}}, "type": "photo", "url": "https://t.co/kwWwPLGrXH"}]}, "card": null, "pl